10 December 
Firstly I thank God for holding me down through all my struggle’s & for the strength 🙏🏾🤞🏾and endless blessings.  Secondly I thank my family for all the love and support they continue to give, I know I’m not always there to share most moments with y’all because I’m always on the road or In studio but I always feel the love and support ❤️🙏🏾 
This year had a lot of challenges & wins.
I thank God for getting me through it all🙏🏾🙏🏾 I’m forever grateful 🙏🏾 and I pray that he continue blessing and protecting me 🙏🏾🙏🏾

To my friends,fans & believers 
Y’all are irreplaceable 🙏🏾🙏🏾🙏🏾
Thank y’all for The endless motivations ,love and endless support you continue to give, I’m forever grateful 🙏🏾
Without y’all I’m almost nothing ❤️

To my girl 
Thanks for holding me down 
Through it all, thanks for being in my corner through my ups and down but mostly through my darkest days
You never left my side 🙏🏾🙏🏾❤️ and for that
I’ll forever respect,love and appreciate you 🙏🏾❤️🔐

To my 2nd family thee crew❤️ @gmp467 it’s been and will always be a blessing to be a part of this team 🤞🏾🔐 
We still got a long way to go a lot of work to do .🙏🏾
God knows I’m forever grateful ❤️🙏🏾

@ghost467 

Aish my broer my bday felt incomplete without you bro. 
The past days before my bday was hard knowing that I wont get to celebrate with you like we always did🤞🏾 I won’t get that bday text from you,
First bday without you homeboy 😔
But I know you popped champagne wherever you are and sent birthday blessings in spirit ❤️
I love and miss you bro 🙏🏾❤️🔐

So all in all Thank you all for the heartfelt birthday wishes I’m forever grateful 🙏🏾❤️

DANKIE🙏🏾
Big House 🙏🏾🙏🏾
